pages.text: Looks like that you click into this page because you have some brilliant ideas about how Cuisine should look like, or you encountered a bug. Either way, you are welcome to file an issue ticket on your $(l:https://github.com/Snownee/Cuisine/issues)issue tracker$(). Alternatively, if you do use Discord, we have a Discord server, too: $(l:https://discord.gg/KzGQW7a)https://discord.gg/KzGQW7a$(); feel free to hop in at any time, and remember to read FAQs and rules before posting things.
